### **4. 27_StreamVizPanel**  
**Description:**  
A real-time dashboard that visualizes streaming data as an animated graph.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamVizPanel - Live Data Visualization

StreamVizPanel helps you visualize live or simulated numeric streams in real time with smooth animations.

## Features
- Animated line graph  
- Easy customization  
- Clean UI for embedded dashboards  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/27_StreamVizPanel.git
cd 27_StreamVizPanel
python visualize.py
